en_146665_0	The owner of Ceylon Today and its sister newspaper Maubima Tiran Alles has been remanded in connection with the Reconstruction and Development Agency (RADA) fraud case.
en_146665_1	Two other individuals, Saliya Wickramasuriya and Jayantha Dias were also remanded together with Alles today in the same Case.
en_146665_2	Colombo High Court ordered to remand them until November 10th.
